erm rentals. Halloween Adventure sells a variety of costumes, masks, makeup, props, hats and other accessories for adults and children. They also sell online as they found costumers would brouse in-store then search online for the best pricing. Its main competition for this group is Halloween Thrills."]], "steps": [{"stage": "router", "label": "SINGLE_HOP", "raw": "SINGLE_HOP 

