ool in Effingham, Illinois. It is located in the Roman Catholic Diocese of Springfield in Illinois. St. Anthony was established in 1874 by the School Sisters of Notre Dame. It is the only Catholic high school in a 50-mile radius.", "Anthony A. Henninger High School is a high school in the Syracuse City School District. Henninger is the largest of the four high schools in this district with a student population of approximately 1,800 people."]], "steps": [{"stage": "router", "label": "MULTI_HOP", "raw": "MULTI_HOP 

